title: 14-Gauge Round Point Shovel with 27 in. Fiberglass D-handle
description: After 35 years, Hisco's mission continues to focus on providing our customers the highest quality professional grade hand tools. The 14-Gauge Round Point Shovel is designed for heavy-duty industrial and contractor work. Features include a fiberglass handle, layered steel blade, and D-Grip for durability and control on the job.
